title: Dev. Update 1.11.17
author: Ghostala√ú
contents: Hello there, Alex here, from Vector7. We're glad to announce a new game update; Map updates: - Fixed falling trought map point on level 14 - Fixed no damage outside the map on various levels - Fixed elveator on level 1; you no longer can get stuck without an elevator on level 1. Characters updates: - Updated Bat Animation - Added early Slime King model (level 16) Achievement updates: - Added a new set of free achievements unlockable when using the cheat for 100 life. Thank you for the time, new levels are coming soon, so stay tuned!
